nodes.text: This Rebel outpost was established by the Alliance to Restore the Republic on the Outer Rim planet Mygeeto during the Galactic Civil War. In 3 ABY, the Galactic Empire learned of the Rebel presence and the Dark Lord of the Sith Darth Vader led an invasion to recapture it. The Imperials were victorious and the outpost was destroyed.
